## 1. Project Identity

Full Hangar (`full-hangar.com`) is an aircraft marketplace intelligence platform — "Carfax for airplanes."
It serves two parallel purposes:
1. A personal deal-finding tool to identify undervalued sub-$50K aircraft to flip for profit.
2. A commercial paid-intelligence product for buyers, brokers, and lenders.

The owner (Ryan) is a licensed pilot with deep aviation domain expertise. He does not write code.
Every agent is responsible for producing working, copy-paste-ready outputs that run on the first try.

