## 13. Known Gotchas & Hard-Won Lessons

| Issue | Resolution |
|-------|-----------|
| Old project folder name included `$` (PowerShell expansion) | Use `FullHangar` under `Documents`; Next.js 16 — do not downgrade |
| Cursor SSRF blocks localhost API calls | Use Open WebUI or terminal for local Ollama — not Cursor directly |
| `createServerClient` vs `createPrivilegedServerClient` | Always prefer privileged for internal routes; anon fallback only as last resort |
| ThemeToggle hydration mismatch | Mounted guard pattern (`ready` state) — never read `localStorage` in SSR |
| GeoIntelMap D3/SSR conflict | Static pre-baked Albers SVG paths — no runtime D3 projection |
| `statement_timeout` on listings browse | Service-role fallback to `aircraft_listings` with indexed columns |
| PostgREST `42P10` upsert conflicts | Fold unknown keys into `raw_data`; fallback to `source_site/source_id` update-or-insert |
| Mixed `intelligence_version` in DB after backfill | Always run `--all` backfill after version bump before shipping |
| Engine model noise (narrative text leaking in) | `sanitize_engine_model()` + `_build_engine_lookup_candidates()` guards — add new tokens there |
| Non-US state codes in geographic data | Backend normalization pass needed — filter/normalize before GeoIntelMap render |
| Controller/GlobalAir challenge gates | Manual CAPTCHA session required per run; use unified browser extension |

